SUCKOW BORAX MINES CONS., Inc., Appellant, v. PACIFIC COAST BORAX CO., Appellee. No. 7628. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 8, 1934. Joseph F. Westall, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Frank L. A. Graham, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
